title: Bug 125809AjTypeDeclaration in the dom shouldn't have the properties of it's subtype AspectDeclaration
description: Bug 125809AjTypeDeclaration in the dom shouldn't have the properties of it's subtype AspectDeclaration
OB: This was shown up whilst building an aspectj for ajdt and a failure in one of the visitor tests.
EB: The AjTypeDeclaration should not have the properties 'privileged' and 'perClause' which it's subtype AspectDeclaration has.
